2026-03-12 19:19:09,969 [DEBUG] trafilatura.main_extractor: discarding element: div None
2026-03-12 19:19:09,969 [DEBUG] trafilatura.main_extractor: extra in p: p And the graph is exponential. As AI agents are able to spend more time acting coherently and consistently with a goal, jobs which solely consist of discrete, well-described, short-horizon tasks—like a software engineer pushing changes to a certain codebase that requires a human check—are the first targets.
2026-03-12 19:19:09,969 [DEBUG] trafilatura.main_extractor: extra in p: p It would, therefore, behoove young people to develop skills that are difficult to replace—sharpening social skills, perhaps, or investing time doing out-of-school projects that leave them in this CEO-like role. (And, while they’re at it, persuade their parents to invest in a little Nvidia).
2026-03-12 19:19:09,969 [DEBUG] trafilatura.main_extractor: extra in p: p In the short-term, many junior white-collar jobs will see massive productivity gains, such as software engineering (where over ninety percent of US-based developers use AI tools in their day-to-day work) or paralegals. But this development also reduces the need for such jobs.
2026-03-12 19:19:09,969 [DEBUG] trafilatura.main_extractor: extra in p: p Work offers structure to our days, meaning to our individual lives, social connections, identity, and a sense of contribution to something larger than ourselves. Many find personal fulfillment and self-actualization through their careers, developing skills that bring satisfaction independent of financial rewards. For countless people, the question “what do you do?” is deeply tied to their sense of self and place in the world. Automation threatens not just livelihoods but these fundamental aspects of identity and purpose.
2026-03-12 19:19:09,969 [DEBUG] trafilatura.main_extractor: extra in p: p 1. Economic Security Without Dependency
2026-03-12 19:19:09,969 [DEBUG] trafilatura.main_extractor: extra in p: p 2. Democratic Access to Technology
2026-03-12 19:19:09,970 [DEBUG] trafilatura.main_extractor: extra in p: p 3. Preserving Meaningful Human Involvement
